Run this command in your terminal in the directory OpenShot was downloaded to verify the SHA256 checksum:
  echo "4ab117270ee8dad8c9d12f57670430dd9fd62a44db5cedc1fa1b06d3aab54c63  OpenShot-v3.5.0-x86_64.AppImage" | shasum -a 256 --check

You should get the following output:
  OpenShot-v3.5.0-x86_64.AppImage: OK